  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      PTSD affects a wide variety of symptoms, some of which have been shown to disrupt family
      relationships. This study will examine some of the effects on parenting, from the
      perspective of the parent with PTSD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
